= Negotiations for a New Cabinet

On April 18 Sartono met to the President to report his failure as *formateur* and returned his mandate in forming a new cabinet. The President is to appoint a new *formateur*.

- @sukiman-sidik: The President has appointed Sidik Djojosukarto and Sukiman Wirjosandjojo..

@sukiman-sidik

The President has announced the names of two new *formateurs*, Sidik Djojosukarto, chairman of the <span style="color: #990000;">**PNI**</span>, and Sukiman Wirjosandjojo, chairman of the <span style="color: #000000;">**Masjumi**</span> party council. The two are expected to form a "coalition cabinet on a broad national basis" in five days with a three day extension.

- @begin: Begin negotiations..

